==== Participants

    - n=200 adults and adolescents with ME/CFS (ages 12–65)
    - Disease duration $gt.eq$6 months
    - Mild to moderate severity (able to participate in quarterly assessments)
    - History of $gt.eq$2 documented infections in prior 12 months (to enrich for infection-prone individuals)
    - Ability to document infections with temporal precision

